::DrillBit::

DrillBit made sure to speak with a soft voice, so he wouldn't upset
KitKat.
"I'm sure it can be recovered. And it's only been a night, so it
shouldn't have gotton to much weather damage. I'm sure we can reconnect
it." He said.
He looked into her eyes, he hadn't had much expieriance with
relationships, or femmbots. But, he was sure that he loved this bot. It
was wierd, he barly new her, but of course love it self is wierd.
There was something about this bot, her personality. She was a Predicon,
but like him, she seemed very kind at hart. He decided to wait untill
she had her leg back, and was relaxed, to make a move on his emotions.
